        {
            "title": "美股期貨上漲 ��靜待美股七巨頭財報與聯準會決議",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DkDpYjpDmIaIJWpMGtgkUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA8400B_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 美國股指期貨週二晚間小幅走高,此前華爾街經歷了疲弱的交易時段,投資者正關注即將到來的「美股七巨頭」財報季和聯準會的政策決議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間20:24(北京時間00:24),標普500指數期貨上漲0.2%至7,185.75點,納斯達克100指數期貨上漲0.4%至27,278.0點。道指期貨上漲0.2%至49,407.0點。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>華爾街因OpenAI憂慮與油價飆升而下跌</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在常規交易時段,標普500指數下跌0.5%,納斯達克綜合指數下跌0.9%,從近期創下的歷史高位回落,科技股領跌。道瓊工業平均指數下跌0.1%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f942d111-e385-3313-9265-6380fcb8292c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次回調源於對人工智慧需求的新擔憂,《華爾街日報》報導稱OpenAI未能達到內部營收和用戶目標,引發市場對數據中心及相關基礎設施大規模支出可持續性的質疑。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">跌幅集中在半導體和人工智慧相關股票,英偉達、超微半導體(Advanced Micro Devices)和博通(<span><span>Broadcom</span></span>)等公司股價下跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">進一步打壓市場情緒的是,油價在週二飆升後仍維持高位,霍爾木茲海峽的中斷持續影響市場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統川普週二表示,伊朗已告知美國他們處於「崩潰狀態」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「他們希望我們『開放霍爾木茲海峽』,越快越好,同時他們試圖解決領導層問題(我相信他們能夠做到!)」,總統在社交媒體上表示。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong><span><span><span><span>微軟</span></span></span></span>、亞馬遜、Alphabet和Meta財報即將公布</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者的焦點現在牢牢鎖定在所謂的「美股七巨頭」財報上,這些公司佔美國股市市值的相當大份額。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">微軟(NASDAQ:MSFT)、Meta Platforms(NASDAQ:META)、亞馬遜(NASDAQ:AMZN)和Alphabet(NASDAQ:GOOGL)將於週三收盤後公布業績,蘋果(NASDAQ:AAPL)將在本週稍後公布。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">預計投資者將仔細審視這些公司能否證明其激進的人工智慧相關資本支出的合理性,特別是在半導體股票和更廣泛科技股近期波動之後。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場也關注聯準會,該央行週二開始為期兩天的政策會議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場普遍預期央行將維持利率不變,但投資者將仔細解讀主席鮑威爾(Jerome Powell)的評論,以尋找有關通膨和經濟增長前景的信號,特別是在與中東緊張局勢相關的油價上漲背景下。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
